stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OpenRegisterPage
    OpenRegisterPage --> FillForm : Enter email, password, name
    FillForm --> ValidateInput : Submit form
    ValidateInput --> ShowValidationError : Invalid input
    ShowValidationError --> FillForm
    ValidateInput --> SendRequest : Valid input
    SendRequest --> CreateUser : POST /api/accounts/register/
    CreateUser --> DuplicateError : Email exists
    DuplicateError --> FillForm
    CreateUser --> UserCreated : Success
    UserCreated --> RedirectLogin
    RedirectLogin --> [*]